pull_request.title: fix: block folder deletion with associated entries and files
pull_request.body:
## Changes
Users should not be able to delete a folder with associated pages, files or entries.
This works correctly for pages, but it is failing for entries and files.

With this PR we block the delegation of folders with associated HCMS entries or files. 
We are creating the following packages in order to not directly add `api-aco` as a dependency to `api-file-manager` / `api-headless-cms` and vice-versa.

Packages created:

- `api-file-manager-aco`
- `api-headless-cms-aco`

Project upgrade needed.

## How Has This Been Tested?
Manually + Jest
